desc: Patisserie and cafe serving a range of bread, cakes, desserts and saviouries baked daily. We partner with Kokako organic fairtrade coffee and have an online shop available.

layout.text: ARTISAN BREADS, DANISHES, TREATS AND MORE

We are passionate about what we do; breads, chocolates, cakes, savouries and sweets are our specialities. We have a small shop and cafe in Birkenhead, Auckland serving delicious Kokako coffee. We are excited to offer you a selection of what we produce to be purchased online, pick up only.
